  "created": "2026-03-16",
  "description": "pitchScatter at maximum 1.0 — every grain ignores the played pitch and fires at a random pitch within the full range. What remains of the played note is nothing. This is a pitched instrument that has renounced pitch. Medium grain size 0.3, moderate density 0.55, low posScatter 0.2 so the randomness is purely harmonic. Low bright filter. Played quietly it sounds like a chord no one chose. Played hard it sounds like all chords simultaneously.",
